ong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人老鮑黃</span></strong></span>就念念不忘」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219b4669a847023362ab9bd4f6aee593eeddbaef","tid":438372,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E9%8D%BE%E6%AC%A3%E6%BD%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%258D%25BE%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E6%25BD%25BC&d=Ev9Lhx4Cu3oRoe4B%2FOjTZk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c816692c\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E9%8D%BE%E6%AC%A3%E6%BD%BC</a><br />\n<br />\n2015年事件<br />\n抽Juno《羅生門》水<br />\n<br />\n2015年7月，麥浚龍（Juno）的新作《羅生門》熱爆網絡，鍾欣潼因為是其過往的「觀音娘娘」，因此亦備受關注。<br />\n<br />\n鍾欣潼先在公開場合否認歌詞內容的女主角是她：「歌曲沒有特定的人，我有在iTunes聽麥浚龍講解。」但她又在Instagram引Juno《念念不忘》的歌詞：「其實你是一幅畫，狠狠往這舊人心上掛，現實過得不順嗎，定定望向這畫中曇花，那故事倉猝結束不到氣絕便已安葬，教兩人心裏有道不解的咒沒法釋放」。[27]<br />\n<br />\n其fans當然立即起哄，說：傳得咁勁你係女主角，呢個時候你post實傳得仲勁！」、「念念不忘」、「作為一首歌的女主角也是一種榮幸！」等。不過其他網民則不值她的抽水所為，斥她：「人地紅先抽水」、「當時就玩X人，而家<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人老鮑黃</span></strong></span>就念念不忘」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df397cafa643ca847b269b3c4b0a9f2727db96d","tid":438372,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E9%8D%BE%E6%AC%A3%E6%BD%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%258D%25BE%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E6%25BD%25BC&d=Ev9Lhx4Cu3o